      <para styleclass="Heading1"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">Segment Editor: Segment-Parameters</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_"><text styleclass="Heading3_atocs_" translate="true">SEGMENT-EDITOR : Segment-Parameters</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">The</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" style="font-style:italic;" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Separator-Header" translate="true"> Segment Parameters </text><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true"> separator shows </text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">with many (not ALL) </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-Motion-Cam-Laws" anchor="Standard" styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Traditional Motion-Laws</link><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">The </text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">Segment-Parameters</text><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">, </text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">when</text><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true"> they show, are unique to the </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Motion-Law</text><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">The best way to learn about the </text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">Segment-Parameters</text><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true"> is to experiment.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Table"><table styleclass="AStandard" rowcount="3" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Image Caption"><image src="SE-SegmentParameters.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"><caption translate="true"><![CDATA[Segment-Parameters of the Since-Constant-Cosine Motion-Law]]></caption></image></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">The image above shows the three </text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">Segment-Parameters</text><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true"> for the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Motion-Cam-Law-Sine-Constant-Cosine-CV" styleclass="Interface2" translate="true">Sine-Constant-Cosine</link><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true"> motion-law. </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">In this case, you can edit the </text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">Segment-Parameters</text><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true"> to give different Motion-Laws that are based on different fractions of the </text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">Segment-Parameters</text><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">For example, Commercial Indexers with a </text><text styleclass="Interface2" translate="true">Modified Sine-Constant-Cosine</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> motion. The </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Constant</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> refers to a period of ZERO-Acceleration, to give Constant-Velocity.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">A family of commercial indexers may include, within the index-period, a </text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" style="font-style:italic;" translate="true">Constant-Velocity of</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> 20%, 33%, 50%, or 66% &#160;of an Indexing Motion Segment.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">In </text><text styleclass="VariableName-IT" translate="true">MotionDesigner</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">, you can specify </text><text styleclass="Body Text" style="color:#ff0000;" translate="true">any</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> percentage of </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Constant Velocity</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Notes" translate="true">NOTE</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">: The </text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">Constant-Fraction</text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">parameter above, refers to the </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Non-Zero Constant Acceleration, </text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">and not the </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Zero Constant-Acceleration</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">.</text></para>
        </td>
